1. Download boost c++
2. Download quantlib
3. load quantlib to IDE( I am using VS 2014) by double click QuanLib_vc14.sln
4. Setup boost c++ path in Property->VC++ Directories
  a. Include Directories -> boost c++ folder
  b. Library Diectories -> boost c++ lib folder
5. Build solution (it may take hours)

please step in youtube for more detail:<br>
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uWMT78XJFJE
